name: Dungeon Duel
overview: Armed with only a magic sword and your own swift feet, you must descend into the dungeons of doom. There you must use your cunning and speed to slip through the treacherous corridors as you steal your way past the dreadful guardians the fiendish One-Eyed Monohopper, Roundwalker, and Mongion Gorks to retrieve the - prized Jewels of Rangor. Non-stop, fast action. For the stout-hearted explorer who must secure the jewel located on each of the maze levels before he will be able to find and open the door leading to the other levels. This program will auto-load. DUNGEON DUEL • Intense Arcade Action • A Super Graphic Game • Real Time • Machine Language Speed • Full Colors and Sound • Competition Scoring Multi Level Dungeon For One Player Ages 12 to Adult • Requires 1 Joy Stick
